    "However, when translated and encoded into LLMs used for social chatbots, these rules of engagement become detached from the contexts and constraints that affect human-to-human interactions (as well as the individual circumstances that might dictate a person's response to another person's moods or expressions of affection).There are a few key traits that improve the experience of user-chatbot interactions.",
